{"tid":1968734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"50K訂閱-細B: 我拍YouTube唔係為左賺錢","createTime":"2020-04-12T01:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T11:25:48.000Z","uid":150921,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f564afad6a03322de88319e5d09505f6035f64e","tid":1968734,"uid":150921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQBn0YC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQBn0YC.png&h=e99c4da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拍YouTube 緊係唔係為左賺錢啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你拍YouTube都賺唔撚到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2o5YLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2o5YLJ.png&h=29d0406d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁拍YouTube 為左咩? 我用圖片答你<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpDE3dG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpDE3dG.png&h=9c992475&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n成個channel 頭18條片 有8條 差唔多一半係有關夾公仔<br />\n用返佢屌大J果句: 你既目的係乜野呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再講下開業成本:<br />\n720k+14k+150k+<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">300k (硬幣)</span></span>+100k<br />\n我都讀得書少 有冇巴絲話我知30萬硬幣點計落開業成本??<br />\n即係假設左30萬變左硬幣就無左金錢既價值?<br />\n定還是係30萬變哂5蚊就會自己有腳碌走左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢描述到夾公仔機係一個專業咁, 要識好多野 要有好多技能<br />\n係比一D有興趣既新手台主<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">實習</span></span><br />\n如果我都做台主<br />\n我想問係咪可以拎黎寫係CV 到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------